749
00:36:27,510 --> 00:36:30,440
Palagi akong susuko.

750
00:36:33,550 --> 00:36:36,760
Ito ay dahil mula sa kaibuturan ng aking puso,

751
00:36:37,230 --> 00:36:38,840
Tunay kitang nirerespeto,

752
00:36:39,760 --> 00:36:41,360
at malalim ang aking nararamdaman

753
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:44,480
